display.title: Chapter I - Just Getting Started!
display.description:
Thank you for playing! and I hope you enjoyed this modpack! I spent hundreds of hours curating this experience, but I may not have been able to perfect it. If you have any suggestions for changes or new additions, please join the Discord in the main menu and let me know! I'm always looking to improve my projects in any way I can.

Inspired by the likes of Elden Ring, Terraria, Devil May Cry, Lord of The Rings, Raspberry Flavoured, and Nine Sols.

Personal Credits - NineRavens, GrayGravity, MysterWobble, SociopathicFungusGirl, Apenaz, Excelsus, Raspmary, Pixion Noelledotjpg, CWdotpng, EvanBones, and BergieBerg.
